title: U-Boat.War.EP02-Attack.America
description:
Have a nice day!

Episode Two - Attack America
From New York to Florida, Americans were unaware that just a few miles off their 
shores, Hitler&#039;s U-boats lurked ready to strike against their country. The 
German U-boat fleet terrorized American coastal waters and vessel after vessel 
went down in one of the greatest maritime disasters of all time.
